data.description: Located in one of the best neighborhoods in Fernley this Desert Lakes home offers golf course living at a fraction of the price. This well maintained home boasts high ceilings, tons of natural lighting, and even comes fully landscaped. Multiple areas of the home allow you to take in views of the golf course and beautiful Sierra mountains that can be enjoyed in all seasons. Just under 2100 sqft. just waiting for your homey touches! Schedule your tour today! Buyer and Buyers Agent should verify all information on MLS
